&lt;p>Unit of an idea is a thought &lt;br>
A thought of love, respect, value, care, preservation, etc. &lt;br>
Let’s call this X thought. &lt;br>
Or thought of disrespect, discouragement, carelessness, demolition, etc. &lt;br>
Let’s call this Y thought.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Based on our understanding of life, &lt;br>
the environment around and our value system, &lt;br>
We may choose to apply X thought &lt;br>
or Y thought on the concepts of &lt;br>
nation, a particular religion, caste of people, color of people, &lt;br>
geography of people, nationality of people, &lt;br>
praying method of people, and the belief system of the people.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>